41">将在她的新纪录片《Megan Thee Stallion: In Her Words》中公开谈论 Tory Lanez 枪击事件</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/megan-thee-stallion-announces-new-documentary-in-her-words-3802734"><em>。</em></a></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/megan-thee-stallion-announces-surprise-new-album-megan-act-ii-coming-next-week-3804197">梅根·西·斯塔林 (Megan Thee Stallion) 宣布将于下周推出令人惊喜的新专辑《MEGAN: Act II》，</a>该消息首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
